# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# INTENTIONALLY NOT IGNORED (committed to repo)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# chroma_db/                 ← vector DB, required at runtime
# SBP_Documents/             ← regulatory PDFs
# outputs/deployment/        ← model.pkl, scaler.pkl, model_meta.json
# outputs/models/            ← xgboost/rf/nn/lr .pkl + scaler.pkl
# outputs/metrics/           ← all JSON + CSV metric files
# outputs/plots/             ← all evaluation .png files
# outputs/ablation/          ← ablation_results.csv + plots
# outputs/experiments/       ← experiment CSVs
# outputs/rag/               ← sample RAG output txts + eval CSVs
# .streamlit/config.toml     ← theme config (no secrets here)
